definitions.Financial Product or Service:
any product, service, plan, or program represented, expressly or by implication, to:
   A. provide any consumer, arrange for any consumer to receive, or assist any consumer in receiving, a loan or other extension of credit;
   B. provide any consumer, arrange for any consumer to receive, or assist any consumer in receiving, credit, debit, or stored value cards;
   C. improve, repair, or arrange to improve or repair, any consumer's credit record, credit history, or credit rating; or
   D. provide advice or assistance to improve any consumer's credit record, credit history, or credit rating.
